## Key Concepts
- CIDR overlap validation in Terraform
- Module input validation
- CI gates using plan
- Multi-env network design

## Code Example
```terraform
variable "environment_cidrs" {
  type = map(string)
  validation {
    condition = alltrue([
      for env, cidr in var.environment_cidrs : cidr != "" && !contains(var.allocated_cidrs, cidr)
    ])
    error_message = "CIDR overlaps with allocated CIDRs or is empty"
  }
}
variable "allocated_cidrs" {
  type = set(string)
  description = "CIDRs already allocated to prod/staging"
}
```

